WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:03.980
<v Audio Descriptions> A man sat at a desk starts watching a video on his computer. 

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:13.680
<v Audio Descriptions> The video on his computer shows a person speaking to the camera.

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:14.220
<v Audio Descriptions> It is playing with no audio.

00:00:18.285 --> 00:00:18.295
<v Audio Descriptions> The man watching the video has a hearing aid.

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:22.420
<v Audio Descriptions> He turns on captions for the video playing.

00:00:30.165 --> 00:00:30.195
<v Audio Descriptions> Another man is watching the captioned video with a group of people chatting away next to him.

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:34.440
<v Audio Descriptions> Turns out that they are in a library.

00:00:34.440 --> 00:00:34.840
<v Audio Descriptions> The group is shushed by the librarian.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:35.300
<v Audio Descriptions> The video is shown playing with the captions on.
